snippet.title: Diana and Roma YES or NO Challenge
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma have fun playing Yes or No Challenge. They need to answer Yes or No to an action unknown to them. It can be something pleasant or not very tasty or not tasty, will they be able to guess? A fun family game to cheer up!
Thanks for watching!
